==Popular culture==
*Portrayed by Kim Yoon-hyung in the 1981 KBS1 TV Series &quot;Daemyeong&quot;.
* Portrayed by Tang Guoqiang in the 2003 TV series &quot;The Affaire in the Swing Age.&quot;
