<doc id="266082" wikidata="Q6890391" url="?curid=266082" title="Mog (TV series)">
<text>Mog was a British television comedy from 1985 to 1986 about a cat burglar living in a psychiatric hospital. It starred Enn Reitel as the title character, who is only faking insanity. It was based on Peter Tinniswood&#x27;s 1970 novel of the same name. It was made for the ITV network by WitzEnd for Central.

