* : Knight Grand Cross of the Royal and Distinguished Spanish Order of Charles III (8 November 2008)
** Knight Grand Cross of the Royal Order of the Crown of Tonga (1 August 2008)
** Coronation Medal of H.M. King George Tupou V (1 August 2008)
* : Member First Class of the Order of Zayed (23 January 1995)
* : Stranger Knight Companion of the Most Noble Order of the Garter (25 June 2024)

